Package: ggmultivar
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate Analysis Plots Using ggplot2 Syntax
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Jannik Vindeloev
Maintainer: Jannik Vindeloev <jannik.vindeloev@example.com>
Description: Create scores and loading plots for multivariate analysis (PCA, PLS) using ggplot2 syntax with custom geoms like geom_scores(), geom_loadings(), geom_conf(), and facet_components(). Compatible with mixOmics objects.
